---
import '../styles/tokens.css';
---

<section class="projects wrap" id="proyectos" data-reveal>
  <span class="sec-eyebrow">// proyectos</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Lo que ya hemos construido</h2>
  <p class="sec-desc">Producto real, en manos de usuarios reales — no mockups de relleno.</p>

  <div class="projects-grid">

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-window-bar">
        <div class="project-window-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <span class="project-tag">App Store · iOS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-shot">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source src="/videos/smash.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="project-info">
        <h3>SMASH</h3>
        <p>La red social hecha por y para jugadores de pádel.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a class="project-card" href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/77Geb3Ka" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <div class="project-window-bar">
        <div class="project-window-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <span class="project-tag">TestFlight · iOS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-shot">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source src="/videos/nook.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="project-info">
        <h3>NOOK</h3>
        <p>El Airbnb del trastero: alquila espacio que no usas, encuentra el que necesitas.</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="https://www.volea.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <div class="project-window-bar">
        <div class="project-window-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <span class="project-tag">Web · SaaS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-shot">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source src="/videos/volea.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="project-info">
        <h3>Volea.io</h3>
        <p>Gestiona tu club de pádel sin Excel, sin WhatsApp, sin líos.</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="https://www.usegateflow.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <div class="project-window-bar">
        <div class="project-window-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <span class="project-tag">Web · SaaS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-shot">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source src="/videos/getflow.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="project-info">
        <h3>Getflow</h3>
        <p>Onboarding de clientes sin emails perdidos ni pasos olvidados.</p>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects {
    padding-top: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 70px;
  }
  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .project-card {
    background: var(--bg-raised);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .project-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--line-strong);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .project-window-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--line);
  }
  .project-window-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 5px;
  }
  .project-window-dots span {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--line-strong);
  }
  .project-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .project-shot {
    background: #1a1a18;
  }
  .project-shot video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 260px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .project-info {
    padding: 18px 20px 22px;
  }
  .project-info h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .project-info p {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
  }

  [data-reveal] {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  [data-reveal].is-revealed {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
